# Frontend Conventions

## Structure

- `static/js/app.js` - main app logic, no framework
- `static/css/style.css` - CSS variables in `:root`, dark theme with teal accent
- `templates/index.html` - single-page dashboard

## Styling

- Use CSS variables: `--accent`, `--text-primary`, `--text-secondary`, `--bg-card`, `--border`.
- Metric rows: `.metric-row` with `.metric-key` (label) and `.metric-value` (value).
- Labels in Portuguese for user-facing text.

## PDF Report Labels

- All metric labels must be in Portuguese. Map keys in `pdfV2Labels` (app.js) and `labels` for flat pdf_report.
- Use descriptive labels: "FC noturna (bpm)" not "overnight_hr_bpm", "Massa Ă³ssea (kg)" not "bone_mass_kg".

## Adding New UI Blocks

1. Add HTML in `templates/index.html` with appropriate ids.
2. Add render logic in `renderDashboard()` in app.js.
3. Add styles in style.css if needed.
